Dari lagu pertama aja udah keren banget, guys. Kerasa nggak sih semangatnya?
Even from the first song it's been so cool, guys. Can you feel the passion?

177
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:05,972
Seru banget ya? Iya nggak sih? Iya nggak sih?
So much fun, right? Isn't it? Isn't it?

178
00:15:05,972 --> 00:15:06,972
Banget! Parah sih.
Definitely! It's crazy.

179
00:15:06,972 --> 00:15:08,372
Ada adrenalin rush kan ya?
There's an adrenaline rush, right?

180
00:15:08,372 --> 00:15:09,672
Pengen lari aku rasanya nih.
I feel like running right now.

181
00:15:10,472 --> 00:15:12,672
Woi, woi, woi, woi! Mau ke mana?!
Hey, hey, hey, hey! Where are you going?!

182
00:15:12,672 --> 00:15:14,372
Mau ke mana? Mau ke mana?!
Where are you going? Where are you going?!

183
00:15:14,372 --> 00:15:18,472
Yah, yah, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop!
Hey, hey, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop!

184
00:15:18,472 --> 00:15:20,972
Nanti keringetan lho! Nanti keringetan.
You'll get all sweaty! You'll get sweaty.

185
00:15:20,972 --> 00:15:23,472
Aduh. Kalo Kaela gimana?
Phew. How about you, Kaela?

186
00:15:23,472 --> 00:15:24,672
Aduh, seru banget.
Man, it's so much fun.

187
00:15:24,672 --> 00:15:27,872
Aku nggak nyangka sih sampe aku bisa ada di sini ya.
I never thought I'd be able to be here.

188
00:15:27,872 --> 00:15:30,672
Tapi ini ngomong-ngomong konsernya masih panjang banget.
But by the way, this concert is still very long.

189
00:15:30,672 --> 00:15:33,172
Jadi kalian tetep semangat ya sampe akhir!
So stay enthusiastic until the end!

190
00:15:33,172 --> 00:15:34,172
張り切ろう！
Let's stay fired up!

191
00:15:34,172 --> 00:15:37,472
Semangat, semangat, semangat, semangat!
Stay fired up, go, go, go!

192
00:15:37,472 --> 00:15:39,972
Eh, tapi ngomongin konser dari tadi...
But we've been talking about the concert...

193
00:15:39,972 --> 00:15:42,672
...emang pada tahu judul konsernya apa?
...but do you guys know the title?

194
00:15:42,672 --> 00:15:47,872
Judul konser kita kali ini adalah "Chromatic Future"!
Our concert title this time is "Chromatic Future"!

195
00:15:47,872 --> 00:15:50,672
Ada yang tahu nggak artinya apa? Ayo absen!
Does anyone know what it means? Sound off!

196
00:15:50,672 --> 00:15:54,172
Nah, ini... Kobo paling tahu.
Now, this... Kobo knows best.

197
00:15:54,172 --> 00:15:58,172
Nih, ah... yang jelasin yang paling tinggi.
Well... the tallest one should explain.

198
00:15:58,172 --> 00:16:00,672
Yuk, let's go!
Come on, let's go!

199
00:16:00,672 --> 00:16:02,672
Segitu ya? Ya udahlah, ya udahlah.
Is that how it is? Fine then, fine.

200
00:16:02,672 --> 00:16:04,972
Nih ya, guys ya, buat kalian yang belum tahu...
Alright, guys, for those of you who don't know...

201
00:16:04,972 --> 00:16:07,172
"Chromatic Future" itu artinya tuh...
"Chromatic Future" means...

202
00:16:07,172 --> 00:16:09,472
...masa depan yang berwarna-warni.
...a colorful future.

203
00:16:09,472 --> 00:16:12,672
Jadi karena Hololive Indonesia kan udah lima tahun nih.
So, since Hololive Indonesia is already five years old.

204
00:16:12,672 --> 00:16:15,972
Kita sama-sama dari hari satu sampe sekarang.
We've been together from day one until now.

205
00:16:15,972 --> 00:16:18,972
Nah, jadi itu untuk ke depannya kita tuh harapannya...
So, for the future, our hope is...

206
00:16:18,972 --> 00:16:23,672
...kita bisa nyiptain waktu dan memori yang berwarna-warni...
...we can create colorful times and memories...

207
00:16:23,672 --> 00:16:27,172
...sama seluruh fans dari Hololive Indonesia!
...with all the Hololive Indonesia fans!

208
00:16:27,172 --> 00:16:30,672
Ya gitu! Betul Kaela Kovalskia! Catat, catat!
That's right! Correct, Kaela Kovalskia! Note it down!

209
00:16:30,672 --> 00:16:32,672
Iya, iya, iya, iya!
Yes, yes, yes, yes!

210
00:16:34,172 --> 00:16:36,472
Nah, kalian sekarang udah pada tahu 'kan?
So, you all know now, right?

211
00:16:36,472 --> 00:16:38,672
Karena tadi udah dijelasin sama Kaela.
Because Kaela explained it earlier.

212
00:16:38,672 --> 00:16:41,472
Kalo gitu, konsernya 'kan udah mulai nih.
In that case, the concert has already started.

213
00:16:41,472 --> 00:16:44,472
Kalian mau nge-post soal konser ini di medsos...
If you want to post about this concert on social media...

214
00:16:44,472 --> 00:16:50,172
jangan lupa hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture ya!
don't forget the hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture!

215
00:16:50,172 --> 00:16:53,172
Karena kita pengen banget lihat kalian tuh...
Because we really want to see your...

216
00:16:53,172 --> 00:16:58,672
apa sih? Pengen lihat semangat kalian!
what's it called? We want to see your passion!

217
00:16:59,672 --> 00:17:02,672
Ya, itu! Betul banget, iya nggak?
Yes, that! Absolutely right, isn't it?

218
00:17:03,172 --> 00:17:04,972
Jangan typo, jangan typo!
Don't make typos, don't make typos!

219
00:17:05,472 --> 00:17:08,672
Asyik! Share ke semua, oke?
Awesome! Share it with everyone, okay?

220
00:17:09,472 --> 00:17:12,172
Tapi, jujur deh. Kalian tuh pas dibilang...
But, honestly. When you were told...

221
00:17:12,172 --> 00:17:14,172
kita bakal konser lho di Indonesia,
we were going to have a concert in Indonesia,

222
00:17:14,172 --> 00:17:16,172
kalian pada kaget nggak sih?
were you guys surprised?

223
00:17:16,172 --> 00:17:18,172
Halo? Ada yang dengerin?
Hello? Is anyone listening?

224
00:17:18,172 --> 00:17:21,172
Oh, iya, iya! Betul! Aku setuju juga.
Oh, yes, yes! Right! I agree too.

225
00:17:21,672 --> 00:17:24,672
Aku merasakan empati terhadap...
I felt empathy for...

226
00:17:24,672 --> 00:17:28,172
...ini, adik saya Zeta.
...well, my little sister Zeta.

227
00:17:28,172 --> 00:17:30,172
Iya empati, iya, iya.
Yeah, empathy, sure, sure.

228
00:17:30,172 --> 00:17:31,672
Kalo Kaela gimana, Kaela Kovalskia?
How about you, Kaela Kovalskia?

229
00:17:31,672 --> 00:17:34,172
Aku juga waktu itu nggak nyangka banget kayak...
I also didn't expect it at all, like...

230
00:17:34,172 --> 00:17:36,172
"Hah? Beneran? Ini riil nih?" gitu 'kan?
"Huh? Really? Is this real?" right?

231
00:17:36,172 --> 00:17:38,672
Kayak "Lho, bisa gitu? Akhirnya!"
Like "Wait, how? Finally!"

232
00:17:38,672 --> 00:17:42,672
Mana udah bersembilan di Indonesia pula, 'kan?
Especially since all nine of us are in Indonesia, right?

233
00:17:43,172 --> 00:17:44,172
Keren banget!
So cool!

234
00:17:44,172 --> 00:17:46,672
Keren banget, iya!
So cool, yes!

235
00:17:46,672 --> 00:17:50,672
Ini 'kan konser pertama Hololive Indonesia yang bersembilan.
This is Hololive Indonesia's first concert with all nine.

236
00:17:50,672 --> 00:17:54,172
Sebenernya tuh nggak hanya ini tuh momen terbesar
Actually, this is not only the biggest

237
00:17:54,172 --> 00:17:56,172
dan terpenting juga untuk fans
and most important moment for fans

238
00:17:56,172 --> 00:17:58,172
Hololive Indonesia...
of Hololive Indonesia...

239
00:17:58,172 --> 00:18:02,672
tapi seluruh dunia juga pasti bakal nonton, nggak sih?
but the whole world will surely watch it too, right?

240
00:18:02,672 --> 00:18:06,672
Iya nggak? Jawab!
Don't you think? Answer me!

241
00:18:08,172 --> 00:18:11,172
Iya, iya! Makasih, makasih semuanya.
Yes, yes! Thank you, thank you everyone.

242
00:18:11,172 --> 00:18:13,672
Eit, tapi tentu aja ini pencapaiannya
Wait, but of course this achievement

243
00:18:13,672 --> 00:18:16,172
nggak bakal cuma sampe di sini aja 'kan?
won't just stop here, right?

244
00:18:16,172 --> 00:18:18,672
Jadi next-nya mungkin kita bisa apa ya?
So next, maybe we can... what?

245
00:18:18,672 --> 00:18:21,672
Dominating the world, gitu!
Dominate the world!

246
00:18:21,672 --> 00:18:26,172
We are ready! Ready, ready, ready, ready!

247
00:18:26,172 --> 00:18:27,672
Betul banget, Kaela, Zeta!
Absolutely right, Kaela, Zeta!

248
00:18:27,672 --> 00:18:30,172
Selain dari dukungan fans in this opportunity...
In addition to the fan support on this occasion,

249
00:18:30,172 --> 00:18:32,172
kita juga mau mengucapkan terima kasih
we also want to say thank you

250
00:18:32,172 --> 00:18:33,972
untuk semua sponsor yang mendukung
to all the sponsors who supported

251
00:18:33,972 --> 00:18:35,672
terjadinya konser ini!
the realization of this concert!

252
00:18:35,672 --> 00:18:37,172
Terima kasih!
Thank you!

253
00:18:37,172 --> 00:18:40,172
Terima kasih! Makasih! Makasih semuanya! Uh!
Thank you! Thanks! Thanks everyone! Whoo!

254
00:18:40,672 --> 00:18:43,672
Thank you, thank you, thank you!

255
00:18:43,672 --> 00:18:46,472
Eh, tapi ngomong-ngomong di konser ini...
But by the way, in this concert...

256
00:18:46,472 --> 00:18:49,472
kayaknya ada yang beda nggak sih?
doesn't something seem different?

257
00:18:49,472 --> 00:18:53,172
Ela, kamu nyadar nggak? Soalnya kamu paling peka 'kan?
Ela, did you notice? Since you're the most attentive.

258
00:18:53,172 --> 00:18:55,172
Eits... ya sadarlah.
Wait... of course I noticed.

259
00:18:55,172 --> 00:18:57,172
Kalo Kobo mah nggak bakalan sadar.
Kobo wouldn't have noticed, though.

260
00:18:57,172 --> 00:19:01,172
Nih, nih, nih, nih. Yang beda tuh kali ini tuh model kita.
Here, look. What's different is our models.

261
00:19:01,172 --> 00:19:04,172
Ini model baru nih!
These are new models!

262
00:19:04,172 --> 00:19:13,172
Ooooh! Kawaii! Gemas banget!
Ooooh! So cute! So adorable!

263
00:19:13,172 --> 00:19:16,672
Kamera, kamera! Kameranya deketin ke aku!
Camera, camera! Bring the camera closer to me!

264
00:19:16,672 --> 00:19:17,672
Nah, mulai, mulai...
There she goes...

265
00:19:17,672 --> 00:19:21,172
Iya, nih, nih. Kalian mau lihat keimutan Kobo nih, nih...
Yes, look. You guys want to see Kobo's cuteness...

266
00:19:21,172 --> 00:19:25,172
Oshiri? Eh? Oh... eh, eh, eh!
Butt? Eh? Oh... wait, wait, wait!

267
00:19:25,172 --> 00:19:27,472
Woi, woi, woi, woi!
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

268
00:19:27,472 --> 00:19:30,172
Ini kamera diambil Kobo semua nggak sih?
Is the camera being taken over by Kobo completely?

269
00:19:30,172 --> 00:19:32,672
Ini ke aku juga, aku juga, aku juga!
Look at me too, me too, me too!

270
00:19:32,672 --> 00:19:35,672
Jangan cuma Kobo!
Not just Kobo!

271
00:19:36,172 --> 00:19:39,172
Ichi, ni, san... Hai, owari! Kobo no ban desu!
One, two, three... Okay, finished! It's Kobo's turn!

272
00:19:39,172 --> 00:19:41,472
Stop, stop, stop, stop, stop!

273
00:19:41,472 --> 00:19:46,172
Mulai, mulai... semua kamera diambil!
Starting again... taking all the cameras!

274
00:19:46,672 --> 00:19:48,172
Oke, oke, oke.
Okay, okay, okay.

275
00:19:48,172 --> 00:19:50,672
Kalo gitu...
In that case...

276
00:19:50,672 --> 00:19:53,472
Sampai kehabisan napas!
I'm out of breath!

277
00:19:53,472 --> 00:19:57,672
Jangan rebutan di depan konser!
Don't fight in the middle of the concert!

278
00:19:57,672 --> 00:19:59,172
Haaai...
Okaaaay...

279
00:19:59,172 --> 00:20:01,172
Iya, iya, iya, iya!
Yes, yes, yes, yes!

280
00:20:01,172 --> 00:20:04,172
Hayo, Zeta kalo udah marah galak lho.
Watch out, Zeta is scary when she's angry.

281
00:20:03,816 --> 00:20:05,116
はいよ ゼータが怒ると怖いからね
Alright, because Zeta's scary when she's angry.

282
00:20:03,816 --> 00:20:04,416
Enggak, bukan.
No, it's not.

283
00:20:04,416 --> 00:20:05,316
Tapi kalau Zeta udah ngomong...
But if Zeta has already spoken...

284
00:20:05,316 --> 00:20:06,116
Takut kan?
Scary, right?

285
00:20:06,116 --> 00:20:13,416
もういいや ゼータがカメラを独り占めしちゃダメっていうのは…うーん、しょうがない
Fine, Zeta said I can't hog the camera... well, it can't be helped.

286
00:20:06,116 --> 00:20:07,216
Iya, iya, udah deh.
Yeah, yeah, fine.

287
00:20:07,216 --> 00:20:10,316
Kalau enggak boleh rebutan kamera sama Zeta,
If I'm not allowed to fight for the camera with Zeta,

288
00:20:10,316 --> 00:20:13,116
mmm... shoganai.
mmm... it can't be helped.

289
00:20:13,116 --> 00:20:19,316
ファンのみんなと遊ぼう！さっきみんなからも大きな声もらってたわけだし、今度はこっちがみんなに大きな声をだしたいっす！
Let's play with the fans! Since we got a lot of loud cheers from everyone earlier, now I want us to shout back at everyone!

290
00:20:13,116 --> 00:20:15,616
Kita main aja deh sama penonton-chan.
Let's just play with Penonton-chan.

291
00:20:15,616 --> 00:20:19,316
Kobo pengen deh coba kita teriakin penonton, karena kan tadi mereka sudah teriakin kita.
Kobo wants us to try shouting at the audience, because they already shouted at us earlier.

292
00:20:19,316 --> 00:20:25,816
はいはいはい！ そうっすよ、カエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
Yeah yeah yeah! That's right, don't worry, it won't be as long as Kaela's streaming hours.

293
00:20:19,316 --> 00:20:20,616
Iya, iya, iya.
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

294
00:20:20,616 --> 00:20:25,016
Maksudnya, kita teriakin intro kita bareng penonton-tachi.
I mean, let's shout our intro together with the audience.

295
00:20:25,016 --> 00:20:26,516
Betul!
Exactly!

296
00:20:26,516 --> 00:20:30,316
そう！みんなにじゃなく、みんなとね
そうそう！そういうことっす！
Yeah! Not 'at' everyone, but 'with' everyone.
Yeah yeah! That's it!

297
00:20:26,516 --> 00:20:29,316
Teriaknya bareng penonton, jangan teriakin penontonnya.
Shout with the audience, don't shout at the audience.

298
00:20:29,316 --> 00:20:30,316
Iya, gitu maksudnya.
Yeah, that's what I meant.

299
00:20:30,316 --> 00:20:35,316
だってこれから歌わなきゃいけないからまず声を温存しなきゃでしょ？
Because we have to sing after this, so we should save our voices first, right?

300
00:20:30,316 --> 00:20:32,816
Soalnya kan habis ini kita harus nyanyi,
Because we have to sing after this,

301
00:20:32,816 --> 00:20:35,316
jadi kita harus simpen suara dulu enggak sih?
so shouldn't we save our voices first?

302
00:20:35,316 --> 00:20:42,616
そうっすよ、カエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
That's right, don't worry, it won't be as long as Kaela's streaming hours.

303
00:20:35,316 --> 00:20:38,316
Betul ya. Enggak bakal sama itu, tenang aja
That's right. It won't be that long, don't worry,

304
00:20:38,316 --> 00:20:42,616
enggak bakal selama durasi stream Kaela gitu ya guys ya.
it won't be as long as Kaela's stream duration, okay guys?

305
00:20:42,616 --> 00:20:46,816
まあいい 大声出していいから好きにして
Well fine, you can shout as much as you want, so go ahead.

306
00:20:42,616 --> 00:20:45,316
Ya udahlah, mau teriak-teriak, ya udah.
Well whatever, if you want to shout, fine.

307
00:20:45,316 --> 00:20:46,816
Aku enggak masalah lah, aku ikut.
I don't mind, I'm in.

308
00:20:46,816 --> 00:20:51,816
みんな準備はいいかな？
Is everyone ready?

309
00:20:46,816 --> 00:20:49,816
Gimana nih semuanya, udah siap belum?
How about it everyone, are you ready yet?

310
00:20:50,016 --> 00:20:51,816
Siap enggak?
Are you ready?

311
00:20:52,616 --> 00:20:56,816
もう出来てるのかよ！っね！じゃあここから！
Are you already ready?! Right! Then from here!

312
00:20:52,616 --> 00:20:55,316
Siap nih kayaknya. Oke, Kobo dulu ya.
Seems like they're ready. Okay, Kobo's turn first.

313
00:20:56,816 --> 00:21:03,816
一緒に「BOKOBOKOBOKO!」って叫ぼう！よろしくよ！
Let's shout "BOKOBOKOBOKO!" together! Let's go!

314
00:20:56,816 --> 00:21:00,316
Aku mau kita sama-sama teriak: 'BOKOBOKOBOKO!'.
I want us to shout together: "BOKOBOKOBOKO!".

315
00:21:00,316 --> 00:21:02,316
Oke? Siap ya?
Okay? Ready?

316
00:21:04,816 --> 00:21:08,316
いち、に、さん！
One, two, three!

317
00:21:08,316 --> 00:21:13,816
BOKOBOKOBOKO!

318
00:21:13,816 --> 00:21:18,316
いいわねいいわね！次はゼータ！
Nice, nice! Next is Zeta!

319
00:21:13,816 --> 00:21:16,316
Seka-seka! Giliran Zeta,
Nice, nice! Zeta's turn,

320
00:21:16,316 --> 00:21:18,316
giliran Zeta.
Zeta's turn.

321
00:21:18,316 --> 00:21:24,816
「ミッションスタート！」って言ったら一緒に「スタート！」って言うわね！
When I say "Mission Start!", you all shout "Start!" together, okay?

322
00:21:18,316 --> 00:21:22,316
Pas aku bilang 'Mission Start-o',
When I say "Mission Start-o",

323
00:21:22,316 --> 00:21:24,816
kalian bareng-bareng teriak 'Start-o' ya.
you all shout "Start-o" together, okay?

324
00:21:24,816 --> 00:21:27,316
いい？アアア！ミッション...
Ready? Ahh! Mission...

325
00:21:27,316 --> 00:21:34,816
スタート！
START!

326
00:21:34,816 --> 00:21:37,816
次はカエラ！
Next is Kaela!

327
00:21:34,816 --> 00:21:37,816
Oke, habis ini Kaela.
Okay, next is Kaela.

328
00:21:37,816 --> 00:21:45,816
よしよし！きてみんは、そしてholoh3roも
「holoh3ro!」って言ったら「HU-HA!」で返してね！簡単でしょ？
Alright! Kitemin, and holoh3ro too.
When I say "holoh3ro!", respond with "HU-HA!" Easy, right?

329
00:21:37,816 --> 00:21:42,316
Nih ya buat semua penonton sama Holohiro juga,
Alright, for all the audience and Holohiro too,

330
00:21:42,316 --> 00:21:44,816
kalau misalnya aku bilang 'Holohiro!',
if I say "Holohiro!",

331
00:21:44,816 --> 00:21:45,816
kalian bilang 'Hu-Ha!'. Gampang kan?
you say "Hu-Ha!". Easy, right?

332
00:21:45,816 --> 00:21:49,816
さあさあさあ！準備はいい？ holoh3ro!
Come on, come on! Are you ready? holoh3ro!

333
00:21:45,816 --> 00:21:48,316
Langsung, langsung, langsung.
Come on, come on, come on.

334
00:21:48,316 --> 00:21:49,816
Oke ya, siap ya. Holohiro!
Okay, ready. Holohiro!

335
00:21:50,316 --> 00:21:57,816
HU-HA!

336
00:21:57,816 --> 00:21:59,316
いいわねいいわね！
Nice, nice!

337
00:21:57,816 --> 00:21:59,316
Mantap, mantap!
Great, great!

338
00:21:59,316 --> 00:22:06,816
いいわ、ついに3期生は息ぴったり
そうね、まだまだ元気が余りそうだわ
Nice, Gen 3 is finally in sync.
Yeah, looks like there's still plenty of energy left.

339
00:21:59,316 --> 00:22:02,316
Keren-keren-keren.
Cool, cool, cool.

340
00:22:02,316 --> 00:22:03,316
Akhirnya Gen 3 kompak juga.
Finally, Gen 3 is in sync.

